      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like the \"standard\" doses are way too low to actually do anything quickly. if i really wanted to hit that 50k iu goal just for a few days to feel better, would there be any specific way i should take it? like should i do it all at once in the morning or split it up to make sure my body actually absorbs it all? i just want to know the most effective way to do it since i've already bought the supplements.",
