      "content": "To maximize absorption of such a high dose, you absolutely must take it with a large meal containing dietary fat, as Vitamin D is fat-soluble. Splitting the 50,000 IU dose into two or three separate doses throughout the day is the most effective strategy to prevent immediate overwhelming of your system. However, I must reiterate that this is a high-risk maneuver, and you should be prepared to monitor any adverse effects closely.",
